      "notes": {
        "patternRationale": "The AI-enabled RAG pattern routes all external model provider traffic through a governed AI Gateway  and leverages a vector storage layer for prompt context enrichment. This isolates model integrations,  allowing prompt security filtering and token usage telemetry to be centrally managed.\n",
        "egressIsolation": "Application components do not call external API endpoints directly. Routing LLM interactions  exclusively through the AI Gateway ensures data protection policies (PII scrubbing) and API rate limits  are consistently enforced.\n"
      },
